:markdown-it
  To get started with our new project, we'll need to **change directory** (folder) from our root to wherever you want your code to live. You can use the command `cd` to enter an existing directory. For this demo, our project will live on **Desktop.**

pre
  code(class='bash').
    cd Desktop                              <span class="comment">// Enters your Desktop folder</span>
    <span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> sampleProject && cd sampleProject <span class="comment">// Chains two commands: creating and entering a directory</span>

:markdown-it
